{"tid":2246822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特區政府：芬蘭要向法治及國際社會交代","createTime":"2020-10-17T11:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T16:52:37.000Z","uid":227801,"like":4,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"bdf887177a77ce62ab3124b6adfa14c5194a981a","tid":2246822,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555304-20201017.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555304-20201017.htm&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24haoxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=3eed9d5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555304-20201017.htm&h=b60a9277\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555304-20201017.htm</a><br />\n芬蘭暫停與本港的移交逃犯協定。保安局表示堅決反對，認為芬蘭要向法治及國際社會交代。<br />\n<br />\n保安局認為，芬蘭因為政治目的，以中國制定《香港國安法》為藉口，單方面暫停與香港的移交逃犯協定，屬雙重標準的政治操作，亦公然干涉中國内政，違反國際法和國際關係基本準則，甘心讓犯罪分子逃避法律制裁，亦令芬蘭有機會成為被本港通緝人士嘗試逃避法律責任的地方。<br />\n<br />\n保安局重申，每個國家都有維護國家安全和主權的法例，亦屬職責所在。中國駐芬蘭使館發言人早前表示，中方對於芬蘭有關決定，表示強烈不滿和堅決反對，敦促芬蘭停止以任何方式，干涉香港事務和中國內政，以免損害兩國關係大局。"},{"pid":"30567265c649952fd1681fe00f5dc8292512ef2e","tid":2246822,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T11:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4460666f345eb01429ecf9f9d0b7f164f12d06c","tid":2246822,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T11:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915affa13265be18c8c933b17b4e7fc7e5823c12","tid":2246822,"uid":361751,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T11:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbtXL2G.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbtXL2G.gif&h=7d585365&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c174c07afda4801fa71ac1e609b0075782316de8","tid":